			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64642388">		
		on Sunday July 21, 2024 @09:20AM (<span class="ind"></span><a rel="nofollow" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23395178&amp;cid=64642388">#64642388</a>)
		<small> </small>
